{"word":"G2010 - ἐπιτρέπω - epitrépō - ep-ee-trep'-o - Give leave","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιτρέπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epitrépō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-trep'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Give leave</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உத்தரவு கொடு, இடங்கொடு"},{"paragraph":"1. to turn to, transfer, commit, entrust"},{"paragraph":"2. to permit, allow, give leave"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5157 - τροπή - tropḗ - trop-ay'/5157\">G5157</a>; to <i>turn over</i> (<i>transfer</i>), that is, <i>allow:</i> - give leave (liberty, license), let, permit, suffer.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}